tenoS enO derdnuh ytriht

yM ssertsim' seye era gnihton ekil eht nus;
laroC si raf erom der naht reh spil' der;
fI wons eb etihw, yhw neht reh stsaerb era nud;
fI sriah eb seriw, kcalb seriw worg no reh daeh.
I evah nees sesor ksamad'd, der dna etihw,
tuB on hcus sesor ees I ni reh skeehc;
dnA ni emos semufrep si ereht erom thgiled
nahT ni eht htaerb taht morf ym ssertsim skeer.
I evol ot raeh reh kaeps, tey llew I wonk
tahT cisum htah a raf erom gnisaelp dnuos;
I tnarg I reven was a sseddog og;
yM ssertsim, nehw ehs sklaw, sdaert no eht dnuorg:
   dnA tey, yb nevaeh, I kniht ym evol sa erar
   sA yna ehs deileb htiw eslaf erapmoc.


